      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW MANTRA (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (23.35) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Worth another chance. LONG GULLY ASH (6) jumped from this same draw and was close to the lead throughout before boxing on well and holding a 1.5 lengths third (23.09) at this track over 400m in a Grade 5. Leading player again. TERRIFIC BAZ (2) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at Angle Park over 530m behind My Picasso (31.20) in a Grade 5. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Cannot be underestimated. PRIME VOLTAGE (1) is always hard to beat when drawn in this box.",
